{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075020/extras/Steam_PROMO3_correct.png?t=1739695997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;It's On The Mouse&quot; is a Caf\u00e9 Management game with a Platforming twist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump and run around the tables to help Holly welcome her customers and serve them the right orders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prove yourself to be a great tiny maid to unlock new stages, each new stage adding something new to the game, including:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> New Items, customers and even obstacles with unique mechanics to test your maid skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unlockable characters with their own skills and playstyle, including the adorable little Vtuber guests Ellie Minibot and FairyDuni</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Not all stages are serving stages! Be careful as dangerous bosses will try their best to force little Holly to close her caf\u00e9!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And if you're tired of serving tables, don't worry as the unlockables will be there to offer you a well deserved break, including a minigame fitting a mouse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All this and more awaits you in the game, so come visit Holly's caf\u00e9! And don't worry, the fun is on the mouse!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3075020?t=1739695997","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075020/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739695997","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075020/f759483aefd460d5e8b3beff7cdf4a81985382a6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739695997","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.